<section>

<title>Prerequisites</title>

<para>&MiKTeX; &MIKTEX_VERSION_STR; requires one of the following
&Windows; operating systems:</para>

<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>&Windows7;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsVistaServicePack2; (all editions except Starter Edition)</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsXPServicePack3; (all editions except Starter Edition)</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2008R2;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2008ServicePack2;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2003R2;</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&WindowsServer2003ServicePack2;</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>

<para>Please note that
&MiKTeX; &MIKTEX_VERSION_STR; does not work on legacy &Windows; platforms
(&Windows9xMeNT2000;).</para>

</section>


